      "content": "but it wasn't just a coincidence though. it wasnt even a \"feeling\" like a gut instinct, it was like the mug itself had this aura or a physical weight to it that shouldn't have been there. i know what you're saying about the mind making connections, but i've seen it happen with three different things this week. it's like i'm tuned into a different frequency. how can you be so sure it's just my mind making things up when the physical sensation is so real?",
